Package: rchess
Version: 0.1
Title: Chess Move, Generation/Validation, Piece Placement/
    Movement, and Check/Checkmate/Stalemate Detection
Description: R package for chess validations, pieces movements and check
    detection. Also integrates functions to plot chess boards given a
    Forsyth Edwards and Portable Game notations.
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Joshua Kunst <jbkunst@gmail.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Reto Wyss <reto.wyss.ch@gmail.com> [ctb]",
    "Ogan Mancarci <ogan.mancarci@gmail.com> [ctb]"
    ))    
